{"tid":1693691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Wir sind das Volk! 各位手足，11月9號，柏林圍牆冧咗。我地係咪要做啲嘢？","createTime":"2019-11-04T17:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T16:44:22.000Z","uid":240642,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b357e496c46b08f1b0e0702901a6992a304a2eab","tid":1693691,"uid":240642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:57:32.000Z","msg":"三十年前嘅呢日，東德，共產主義嘅第一塊骨牌，終於倒下。同香港一樣，喺1989年，東德幾乎每星期都有示威。最後佢地斷斷續續示威左<span style=\"color: red;\">42次</span>，先至得到勝利。我地而家面對嘅係中共，<span style=\"color: red;\">你覺得咁快就可以完</span>？<br />\n<br />\n我哋係咪好應該紀念呢個咁重要嘅歷史日子呢？有人已經發起左喇。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">詳情喺下面，同我入去推撚爆佢！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><em>11月9日搞個柏林圍牆倒塌30週年集會</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666722\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666722</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n另外，我想介紹兩句口號畀大家聽：<br />\n<blockquote><em>他們最著名的口號是「我們是人民！（Wir sind das Volk!）」，表示民主共和國須由人民管治，而非由一個聲稱代表人民的非民主政黨管治。</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/週一示威\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E9%80%B1%E4%B8%80%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcRPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=fa6ec1e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/週一示威</a><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n跟我背一次！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Wir sind das Volk!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><em>「推倒這堵牆！」（Tear down this wall!）是美國總統列根在1987年的演說中，對蘇聯共產黨總書記戈爾巴喬夫的呼籲。</em><a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/推倒這堵牆！\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E6%8E%A8%E5%80%92%E9%80%99%E5%A0%B5%E7%89%86%EF%BC%81&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcRPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=aeb31fa0\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/推倒這堵牆！</a><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n跟我背一次！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Tear down the wall!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">星期六，不見不散</span></span>"},{"pid":"342dcd141e99e6324bd6bca723684550c1b86d38","tid":1693691,"uid":161504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:59:53.000Z","msg":"Hallo deutscher Br&uuml;der  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd006dddabbc1c99f1df6078c3ae11100f1cfaab","tid":1693691,"uid":161504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:03:33.000Z","msg":"要教埋大家點讀:<br />\n<br />\nWir: 好似 fear, 但係 f 變 v -&gt; vear <br />\nsind: sin+t音 -&gt; sint <br />\ndas: 達+s -&gt; 達s<br />\nVolk: 伏+k -&gt; 伏k"},{"pid":"e02ed02f8e9a4356f03940d638173213f2fc726f","tid":1693691,"uid":161504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:05:16.000Z","msg":"順便借埋個位，學埋呢個都無妨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAngie hilf uns!!!<br />\n<br />\n東德勝利有賴戈爾巴喬夫，我搵到我地嘅戈爾巴喬夫！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547127\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547127</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"459a03b6338c62f1453b196f2c198cc67dcc5d62","tid":1693691,"uid":240642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd006dddabbc1c99f1df6078c3ae11100f1cfaab","tid":1693691,"uid":161504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:03:33.000Z","msg":"要教埋大家點讀:<br />\n<br />\nWir: 好似 fear, 但係 f 變 v -&gt; vear <br />\nsind: sin+t音 -&gt; sint <br />\ndas: 達+s -&gt; 達s<br />\nVolk: 伏+k -&gt; 伏k"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:06:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝巴打！<br />\n<br />\n連登仔女咁醒，其實唔難架！<br />\n有心學嘅Google YouTube 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37451827449056e3c58262c396ebdd933bd54896","tid":1693691,"uid":240642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:10:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"31a209501975ecbfe7ed6c277e3ed8d